From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000013 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: LoongArch64 Adaptation <loongarch64-adaptation@example.invalid>
Date: Thu, 25 Jun 2026 10:10:00 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] Restore rustix 0.38 termios for LoongArch64 gix-prompt

gix-prompt-0.7.0 imports rustix::termios on Unix. After 0011 removed the
LoongArch64 termios feature entries from rustix-0.38.21, cargo_bazel can get
past the tempfile/rustix path but then fails compiling gix-prompt:

    unresolved imports rustix::termios

Restore the LoongArch64 termios feature entries for both the rust_library and
the rustix build script. The earlier 0011/0012 changes remain in place: the
LoongArch64 branch still selects errno, libc, and linux_raw_sys for rustix's
libc backend.

Reason: gix-prompt is part of the crates-index/gix stack used by cargo_bazel,
so removing rustix termios is too broad. Restoring the feature is the minimal
next step now that the LoongArch64 rustix dependency branch has the backend
deps it was missing.
---
 crate_universe/3rdparty/crates/BUILD.rustix-0.38.21.bazel | 6 ++++++
 1 file changed, 6 insertions(+)

diff --git a/crate_universe/3rdparty/crates/BUILD.rustix-0.38.21.bazel b/crate_universe/3rdparty/crates/BUILD.rustix-0.38.21.bazel
index 79282326..7031fadb 100644
--- a/crate_universe/3rdparty/crates/BUILD.rustix-0.38.21.bazel
+++ b/crate_universe/3rdparty/crates/BUILD.rustix-0.38.21.bazel
@@ -141,6 +141,9 @@ rust_library(
         "@rules_rust//rust/platform:aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu": [
             "termios",  # aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu
         ],
+        "@rules_rust//rust/platform:loongarch64-unknown-linux-gnu": [
+            "termios",  # loongarch64-unknown-linux-gnu
+        ],
         "@rules_rust//rust/platform:aarch64-unknown-nixos-gnu": [
             "termios",  # aarch64-unknown-nixos-gnu
         ],
@@ -428,6 +431,9 @@ cargo_build_script(
         "@rules_rust//rust/platform:aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu": [
             "termios",  # aarch64-unknown-linux-gnu
         ],
+        "@rules_rust//rust/platform:loongarch64-unknown-linux-gnu": [
+            "termios",  # loongarch64-unknown-linux-gnu
+        ],
         "@rules_rust//rust/platform:aarch64-unknown-nixos-gnu": [
             "termios",  # aarch64-unknown-nixos-gnu
         ],
-- 
